title: clone.rar
description:
A bunch of PHP scripts bought from someone on eBay.

These are website clones written in PHP.  The following websites have been cloned:

anonym.to
freedomain.co.nr
google.com
hotscripts.com
imageshack.us
savefile.com
uploadgalaxy.com
whatismyip.com
yousendit.com

There are also tons of more scripts included, all written in PHP.  I have only tested a few (like the Youtube clone) and it works pretty well.  Some are pretty good, others cheap skates.  May require some skill to install certain sites.

Enjoy!
